subSubSection.paragraph:
The median lobe of the male from the Alpi Orobie ( holotype of
T. orobiana
) is characterized by a pronounced crista apicalis and the shape of the ventral process (apically not obliquely truncate, but rounded in lateral view; less slender and medio-apically not incised in ventral view) ( Figs 5 , 22, 28 ).
